arStrings.szText: What a surprise it is to see you under these circumstances, bearing a scroll from my agent no less?
Kharov was one of our most devout servants. It pained me to see him cast his lot with the Burned Knights. But this? (sigh)

When a calf becomes sickly, we cut it down to prevent the spread of infection. Kharov must too be cut down, so his maddened grip never lays claim to Neyrelle or the Soulstone. (sigh) Return to Dmitriy at Faith's Torch, he will assist you in your task.
